http://sourceforge.net/projects/qucs

Compile instructions Linux (Ubuntu):
First make sure you have all packages installed:
build-essential flex bison qt4-dev-tools gperf

Install ADMS 2.3.0:
./configure
make
sudo make install
sudo ldconfig

Compile qucs:
cd qucs
./autogen.sh
make
sudo make install


Compile qucs-core:
cd qucs-core
./bootstrap.sh
./configure --enable-maintainer-mode --prefix=<path/to/install>
make
sudo make install



Note for OS X:

 Recent changes to code ane not yet reflected on the build system.

 Please configure as follows:

$ LIBS=-lc++ CXX=clang++ CXXFLAGS="-stdlib=libc++" LDDFLAGS=-stdlib=libc++ \
./configure --enable-maintainer-mode --prefix=<path/to/instal>
